#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; is an easy to use personal information manager (<acronym>PIM</"
"acronym>). You can write journal entries, schedule appointments, events, and "
"to-dos. &korganizer; will remind you about pending tasks, and help you keep "
"your schedule."
msgstr ""
"El &korganizer; és un gestor de la informació personal (<acronym>PIM</"
"acronym>) de fàcil ús. Podeu escriure entrades al diari, planificar cites, "
"esdeveniments i tasques pendents. El &korganizer; us recordarà les tasques "
"pendents, i us ajudarà a mantenir la vostra planificació."

